<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>名古屋旅行 2025.5.14–16</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#f5f2ed;--bg2:#ffffff;--bg3:#edeae4;
  --ink:#1c1a17;--ink2:#3d3a34;--muted:#7a7265;--faint:#b0a898;--border:#ddd8cf;
  --gold:#8a6d2f;--gold2:#c4a24a;--gold3:#f0e4c0;
  --red:#8b2e20;--red2:#c4442e;--red3:#fdecea;
  --blue:#1e3d6e;--blue2:#2e5fa8;--blue3:#e8f0fb;
  --sage:#2d5c3e;--sage2:#d6ead9;
  --amber:#7a5500;--amber2:#fff4d6;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:300;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;line-height:1.6;}

/* HERO */
.hero{background:var(–ink);min-height:50vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding:60px 24px 68px;text-align:center;}
.hero::after{content:’’;position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 15% 85%,rgba(196,162,74,.12) 0%,transparent 55%),radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 85% 15%,rgba(46,95,168,.1) 0%,transparent 50%);pointer-events:none;}
.hero-inner{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:640px;}
.hero-eyebrow{font-size:10px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.45em;color:var(–gold2);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:18px;display:block;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .7s ease .1s forwards;}
.hero-title{font-family:‘Cormorant Garamond’,serif;font-size:clamp(44px,9vw,84px);font-weight:300;line-height:.95;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:14px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .7s ease .25s forwards;}
.hero-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(–gold2);}
.hero-date{font-family:‘Cormorant Garamond’,serif;font-size:clamp(14px,2.5vw,19px);font-weight:300;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);letter-spacing:.18em;margin-bottom:36px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .7s ease .4s forwards;}
.hero-badges{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:8px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .7s ease .55s forwards;}
.hero-badge{font-size:11px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:5px 13px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);border-radius:20px;}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

/* NAV */
.nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:var(–bg2);border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;box-shadow:0 1px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.06);}
.nav-inner{display:flex;width:100%;max-width:900px;}
.nav-tab{flex:1;padding:13px 6px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;font-size:11px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(–muted);border-bottom:2px solid transparent;transition:all .25s;user-select:none;}
.nav-tab:hover{color:var(–gold);}
.nav-tab.active{color:var(–gold);border-bottom-color:var(–gold);font-weight:500;}
.nav-tab .n{font-family:‘Cormorant Garamond’,serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:300;display:block;margin-bottom:1px;line-height:1.2;}

/* MAIN */
main{max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px 80px;}
.day-section{display:none;}
.day-section.active{display:block;animation:fadeIn .35s ease;}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

/* DAY HEADER */
.day-header{padding:44px 0 24px;position:relative;}
.day-header::after{content:’’;display:block;width:100%;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right,var(–gold2),transparent);margin-top:18px;}
.day-num-large{font-family:‘Cormorant Garamond’,serif;font-size:108px;font-weight:300;line-height:1;color:var(–border);position:absolute;right:0;top:14px;letter-spacing:-.04em;user-select:none;}
.day-tag{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.4em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–gold);margin-bottom:9px;display:block;}
.day-title-text{font-family:‘Cormorant Garamond’,serif;font-size:clamp(24px,5vw,40px);font-weight:300;color:var(–ink);line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-.01em;}
.day-title-text em{font-style:italic;color:var(–gold);}

/* TIMELINE */
.timeline{position:relative;padding-top:4px;}
.timeline::before{content:’’;position:absolute;left:72px;top:0;bottom:0;width:1px;background:var(–border);}
.tl-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:72px 1fr;position:relative;}
.tl-time{text-align:right;padding:17px 15px 17px 0;font-family:‘Cormorant Garamond’,serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:var(–faint);letter-spacing:.04em;line-height:1.4;align-self:start;position:relative;}
.tl-time::after{content:’’;position:absolute;right:-5px;top:24px;width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;background:var(–bg2);border:2px solid var(–border);z-index:1;}
.tl-item.hl-gold .tl-time::after{background:var(–gold2);border-color:var(–gold2);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(–gold3);width:11px;height:11px;right:-6px;top:23px;}
.tl-item.hl-red  .tl-time::after{background:var(–red2);border-color:var(–red2);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(–red3);width:11px;height:11px;right:-6px;top:23px;}
.tl-item.hl-blue .tl-time::after{background:var(–blue2);border-color:var(–blue2);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(–blue3);width:11px;height:11px;right:-6px;top:23px;}
.tl-body{padding:15px 0 15px 22px;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);}
.tl-item:last-child .tl-body{border-bottom:none;}
.tl-cat{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.28em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:4px;}
.cat-move{color:var(–faint);}.cat-food{color:var(–red);}.cat-spot{color:var(–blue);}.cat-hotel{color:var(–sage);}.cat-tower{color:var(–amber);}
.tl-name{font-family:‘Noto Serif JP’,serif;font-size:14.5px;font-weight:400;color:var(–ink);margin-bottom:4px;line-height:1.5;}
.tl-item.hl-gold .tl-name{color:var(–gold);font-size:15.5px;font-weight:600;}
.tl-item.hl-red  .tl-name{color:var(–red);font-size:15.5px;font-weight:600;}
.tl-item.hl-blue .tl-name{color:var(–blue2);font-size:15.5px;font-weight:600;}
.tl-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(–muted);line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;}
.tl-desc strong{color:var(–ink2);font-weight:500;}
.tl-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;margin-top:7px;}
.tl-tag{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:3px;}
.tag-warn{background:var(–amber2);color:var(–amber);border:1px solid #e8d080;}
.tag-ok{background:var(–sage2);color:var(–sage);border:1px solid #a8d4b0;}
.tag-info{background:var(–blue3);color:var(–blue);border:1px solid #a8c4f0;}
.tag-res{background:var(–gold3);color:var(–gold);border:1px solid #d4b870;}

/* MAP */
.map-wrap{margin:28px 0;border:1px solid var(–border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.06);}
.map-head{background:var(–bg3);padding:11px 18px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–muted);border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;}
.map-container{height:360px;}
.map-container iframe{width:100%;height:100%;border:none;display:block;}
.map-legend{padding:11px 18px;background:var(–bg2);display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(–border);}
.leg-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11px;color:var(–muted);}
.leg-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;}

/* NOTICE */
.notice{border-left:3px solid var(–gold2);background:var(–gold3);padding:12px 16px;margin:16px 0;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8;color:var(–ink2);border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;}
.notice strong{color:var(–ink);font-weight:500;}
.notice-title{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–gold);margin-bottom:4px;}
.notice.blue{border-left-color:var(–blue2);background:var(–blue3);}
.notice.blue .notice-title{color:var(–blue);}

/* CARDS */
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:12px;margin:22px 0;}
.card{background:var(–bg2);border:1px solid var(–border);border-radius:6px;padding:16px;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.04);}
.card-title{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–gold);margin-bottom:9px;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);}
.card-body{font-size:12px;line-height:1.9;color:var(–muted);}
.card-body strong{color:var(–ink2);font-weight:500;}
.card-body a{color:var(–blue2);font-size:11px;text-decoration:none;}
.card-body a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}

/* CHECKLIST */
.checklist-wrap{background:var(–bg2);border:1px solid var(–border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;margin:14px 0;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.04);}
.checklist-head{background:var(–bg3);padding:11px 18px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(–ink2);border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);}
.checklist-item{display:flex;gap:13px;padding:12px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);align-items:flex-start;font-size:12px;color:var(–ink2);line-height:1.7;}
.checklist-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.check-box{width:17px;height:17px;border:2px solid var(–border);border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;position:relative;}
.check-box:hover{border-color:var(–gold2);}
.check-box.checked{background:var(–gold2);border-color:var(–gold2);}
.check-box.checked::after{content:‘✓’;position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;}
.check-text strong{color:var(–ink);font-weight:600;}
.check-text small{font-size:11px;color:var(–muted);display:block;margin-top:2px;}

/* GHIBLI DETAIL INTEGRATION */
.ghibli-detail {
background: #fff;
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 8px;
margin-top: 20px;
padding: 20px;
}
.ghibli-detail h3 {
font-family: ‘Noto Serif JP’, serif;
border-bottom: 2px solid var(–gold);
padding-bottom: 8px;
margin-bottom: 15px;
color: var(–gold);
}
.ghibli-sch-row {
display: flex;
gap: 10px;
padding: 8px 0;
border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
font-size: 13px;
}
.ghibli-sch-time {
font-weight: 700;
color: var(–muted);
min-width: 50px;
}
.ghibli-badge {
display: inline-block;
padding: 2px 8px;
border-radius: 4px;
color: #fff;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 700;
margin-right: 5px;
}

footer{background:var(–ink);text-align:center;padding:26px 20px;font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:60px;}

@media(max-width:560px){
.timeline::before{left:58px;}.tl-item{grid-template-columns:58px 1fr;}
.day-num-large{font-size:70px;}.map-container{height:240px;}
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="hero-eyebrow">2025 Spring Trip</span>
    <h1 class="hero-title"><em>名古屋</em><br>旅行</h1>
    <p class="hero-date">May 14 — 16, 2025</p>
    <div class="hero-badges">
      <span class="hero-badge">🌲 ジブリパーク</span>
      <span class="hero-badge">🍱 ひつまぶし</span>
      <span class="hero-badge">🐳 名古屋港水族館</span>
      <span class="hero-badge">🗼 MIRAI TOWER 夜景</span>
      <span class="hero-badge">🥩 とん八 味噌カツ</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <div class="nav-tab active" onclick="show('d1')"><span class="n">01</span>5/14 水</div>
    <div class="nav-tab" onclick="show('d2')"><span class="n">02</span>5/15 木</div>
    <div class="nav-tab" onclick="show('d3')"><span class="n">03</span>5/16 金</div>
    <div class="nav-tab" onclick="show('check')"><span class="n">✓</span>準備リスト</div>
  </div>
</nav>

<main>

<!-- DAY 1 -->

<section class="day-section active" id="d1">
  <div class="day-header">
    <div class="day-num-large">01</div>
    <span class="day-tag">May 14, Wednesday — Day One</span>
    <h2 class="day-title-text">東京 → ジブリパーク<br><em>夕食（ひとはし）</em></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline">
    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-time">06:00</div>
      <div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-cat cat-move">出発</div><div class="tl-name">立会川駅 出発</div><div class="tl-desc">京急で品川駅へ（約10分）。</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-time">06:40</div>
      <div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-cat cat-move">新幹線</div><div class="tl-name">品川駅 — のぞみ5号 乗車</div><div class="tl-desc">品川06:40発 → 名古屋08:10着（所要90分）。</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-time">08:10</div>
      <div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-cat cat-move">到着・受取</div><div class="tl-name">名古屋駅 到着 → JPタワー名古屋10F Times Car 受取</div><div class="tl-desc">名古屋駅直結・徒歩1分。エレベーターで10Fへ。荷物はトランクへ。</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-time">09:00</div>
      <div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-cat cat-spot">到着・待機</div><div class="tl-name">ジブリパーク 西駐車場 到着・待機</div><div class="tl-desc">名古屋駅から車約30〜35分。開園10:00まで駐車場で待機。</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item hl-gold">
      <div class="tl-time">10:00<br>〜<br>17:00</div>
      <div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-cat cat-spot">メインスポット</div><div class="tl-name">🌲 ジブリパーク — 終日満喫（7時間）</div><div class="tl-desc">平日開園<strong>10:00</strong>、閉園<strong>17:00</strong>。水曜は比較的空いている。大倉庫・もののけの里・魔女の谷など。</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-time">17:30</div>
      <div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-cat cat-move">出発</div><div class="tl-name">西駐車場 出発</div><div class="tl-desc">閉園後30分で退場・出発。金山ホテルまで車約40分。</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-time">18:10</div>
      <div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-cat cat-hotel">チェックイン</div><div class="tl-name">ANA Crowne Plaza Hotel Grand Court Nagoya By IHG</div><div class="tl-desc">名古屋市中区金山町1-1-1。金山駅徒歩1分。チェックイン・着替え。</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item hl-red">
      <div class="tl-time">19:00</div>
      <div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-cat cat-food">夕食</div><div class="tl-name">新和食 ひとはし</div><div class="tl-desc">名古屋駅徒歩3分。完全個室和食店。コース料理。<br>営業 17:00〜23:00（LO22:00）</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-time">20:30</div>
      <div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-cat cat-hotel">就寝</div><div class="tl-name">ホテル 帰着・就寝</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="map-wrap">
    <div class="map-head"><span>📍 Day 1 ルートマップ</span><span>名古屋駅 → ジブリパーク → ホテル（金山）</span></div>
    <div class="map-container">
      <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/directions?key=AIzaSyD-9tSrke72PouQMnMX-a7eZSW0jkFMBWY&origin=place_id:ChIJ7cv00DwsDogRAMDACa2m4K8&destination=place_id:ChIJK6iqQlJ3A2ARQfVkGj06ljk&waypoints=place_id:ChIJs9ADAkVnA2ARixLFaXpLFjY&mode=driving&language=ja" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"></iframe>
